# =============================================================================
# .antigravityignore — Context Isolation for yumfood (ServiceNow Agentic SDLC)
# =============================================================================
# Files listed here are excluded from Antigravity's active context window
# to prevent token bloat and protect sensitive configuration.
# NOTE: agentinstructions.md is auto-regenerated by the sn-scriptsync extension
#       and MUST be ignored here rather than deleted.
# =============================================================================

# --- ScriptSync Auto-Generated Files (token-heavy, runtime noise) ---
agentinstructions.md

# --- ScriptSync Internal Mapping & Settings (sensitive runtime state) ---
**/_settings.json
**/_map.json
**/_syncignore.json

# --- Agent API Queue (ephemeral request/response files — never source-of-truth) ---
agent/requests/
agent/responses/

# --- Build & Dependency Artifacts ---
node_modules/
dist/
target/
.now/
*.tsbuildinfo
.jest_cache/

# --- IDE & OS Noise ---
.vscode/settings.json
.DS_Store
*.log
*.swp
*.swo

# --- Autocomplete Cache (large, machine-generated) ---
autocomplete/

# --- Package Lock (large, deterministic — not useful for AI context) ---
package-lock.json
